name: Grad3ph
tagline: Tool for visually creating a schema for graph database.
body:
### Grad3ph
D3 base directed graph database scheme modeler. 
The main purpose of this project is to enable fast and visual creation of database schemes for graph databases. 
Visualizing nodes and edges between them. Setting up node's and edge's properties with default values, types and other.
